NguDumisa Mpupha I join the cries of many South Africans about the plight of women’s degradation which is killing our
generation. May Yahuah be with the soul of Khensani. We work at unfortunate times where men are
the perpetrators of the ruin of women – I mean generally. Siyaliiila ngawe Khensani!!!
Ndiniken’ibhuku ndiyabhala
