Koko ukufa kuse mbizeni Hamba mntwana wethu, ulale kakuhl’emandleni Sohlala sikukhumbula Siyalila ngawe sithi
Mbombo zone zehlabathi sithi
Eli lizwe lilahlekelwe Lucwambu lwengqaka ekamva beliqaqambile
Tyala Yahuwa ithemba lentsasa Kumzi wakwa Khensani nabo baba ngqongileyo
